Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.86,0:01:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前顶叶？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.07,0:01:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:02:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是关于大脑里叫作前顶叶的一部分里\N存在着会引起特定感受的寄生虫的论文
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.58,0:02:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球上存在着无数的寄生生物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.23,0:02:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时还能支配宿主这一现象也会被人们发现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是人们仍顽固地否定有寄生在人体内支配宿主的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.72,0:02:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.27,0:02:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能支配人类  就是说人类的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.66,0:02:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说连思想都被支配
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.79,0:02:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思想？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.14,0:02:42.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  如果思想被寄生虫控制的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.24,0:02:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就简直和鼠疫一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.82,0:02:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说思想会变成和无法治疗的遗传病一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,延续这想法的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会成为人们认可种族灭绝或者是宗教压制的大屠杀的论调
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:04.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  谈论脑内寄生虫一直是战后的禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  脑内寄生虫一定是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.45,0:03:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这个要爷爷来证明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.44,0:03:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  虽然是打算继续努力…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:28.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能活着证明学说的科学家是非常稀少的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.88,0:03:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我的研究受到正当的评价
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候  就算我这身体已经风骨不存
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:42.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能召回我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召回是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像神一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那个时候  爷爷就会成为神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.73,0:04:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果…果然用这鸡屋的锁是打不开的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手  回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:15.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠理子  别着急
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这钥匙能打开对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试过了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钥匙没错  只是有点卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:30.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠理子  有人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:35.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这钥匙能打开的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:37.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试过了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.89,0:04:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开的话  就能获得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能对这地狱说再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:46.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠理子  有人过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作快点  快点…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边先放下！快来看这边的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:17.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  妈妈在哪里  在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美代子  听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:35.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和妈妈都在战争中失去了亲人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  爸爸死了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有人…能照顾你了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.87,0:05:48.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…死去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去依靠高野老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.28,0:06:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高野…一二三老师  去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高野…一二三
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.07,0:06:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是高野老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.42,0:06:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的恩师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:19.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定会照顾…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:20.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.81,0:06:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生  恶化了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:32.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  快点去手术室
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:33.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.28,0:06:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.93,0:06:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  能照顾你的人是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.44,0:06:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高野一二三
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.11,0:06:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.49,0:06:57.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲戚的人之类的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.37,0:07:13.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:35.04,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}对不起…对不起…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:39.48,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}为什么  为什么你连这种事情都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:47.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}对不起…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棺…棺箱之刑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.45,0:07:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  但是看护说还有更好的方法就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:50.36,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:58.37,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}对不起…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.16,0:08:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  快点吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.34,0:08:17.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.99,0:08:19.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很浪费吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:21.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.59,0:08:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快吃  还有剩的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.35,0:08:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  有谁知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山的对面有儿童教导设施
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里还有点心时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.67,0:08:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,院长是非常温柔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:44.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都叫她妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要再待在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去有妈妈的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家如果有机会的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想逃走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能逃走的话  当然想了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.84,0:09:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  一定会被抓住的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.63,0:09:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连去外面都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.94,0:09:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都上锁了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:18.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有地方都被锁上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是除了一个地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里院鸡屋的锁  和楼梯深处紧闭门的锁是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.79,0:09:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠理子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道要把钥匙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.42,0:09:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要了  很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  一个人是危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.09,0:09:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  大家一起的话  就能有所改变
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:47.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:50.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前  发生过集体逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.68,0:09:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.10,0:09:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他们保密来着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那个时候被抓住的似乎只有一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道为什么只被抓住了一个就完事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们四散逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何  要试试看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:14.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.18,0:10:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:19.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.11,0:10:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被抓住的话一定会被杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.03,0:10:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你打算一直都待在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  不要  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你们害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  这是仅有一次的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.48,0:10:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要拥有仅有一次的勇气就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美代子  你如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对能逃走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有绝对保证的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:10:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  你能一起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我一个人逃走来说  概率确实增高了许多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.17,0:11:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  对你来说也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何  美代子	
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  在那里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.50,0:11:22.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人逃走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住  站住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.16,0:11:35.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  按计划那样各自向四周逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.80,0:11:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.49,0:11:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把我的手指…手指给…！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.95,0:13:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您了  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不会忘记您的恩情的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.36,0:13:12.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱应该由人生的路还很长的年轻人拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.87,0:13:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样的老头子拿着也没有用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好珍惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是羡慕高野君能有这么好的一个孙女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定正在九泉之下向别人炫耀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有作出任何值得让他炫耀的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.19,0:13:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想只有当我完成了祖父的研究  我才有权利让祖父来夸奖我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三四你努力至今已经很不容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以礼待人  获得了许多人的信赖和支持
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:51.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这笔钱交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.47,0:14:02.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就意味着我承认你就是高野君的研究正式的继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在此致以深深的谢意  谢谢您了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时的我到最后还是什么忙都没有帮上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这也是我对高野君的一种赎罪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为能有这样的好朋友  祖父他也会很幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我还有一口气在  就绝不会让三四你的研究有任何的障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到什么的话就尽管来找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会全力帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到这样的研究居然被埋没了数十年…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.02,0:14:52.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说军方的上层部都没有理睬这项研究
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.27,0:15:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以谁都不知道  也没有被GHQ进行追究吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.27,0:15:00.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（GHQ(General Headquarters)  联合国最高司令总官司令部  暨二战后占领日本的联合国军司令部）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.05,0:15:09.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这简直像是高野老师借用了你的身体继续进行着研究呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许真的是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也经常感叹这奇妙的因缘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹰野小姐  请不要误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这项研究的目的不在于保有这项细菌武器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.83,0:15:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是为了针对这种细菌的危险性  作出充分的事前准备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.83,0:15:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.39,0:15:36.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  理事会还提出了几个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.51,0:15:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其一是委托一个对于此项研究拥有优秀能力的人进行指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我直言  但是请问你们认为还有人比我更了解这项研究吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.29,0:15:57.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹰野小姐  冷静一点  冷静一点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.23,0:16:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们当然不会让你为难
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.78,0:16:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定用什么人的权利在我这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.81,0:16:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以鹰野小姐只要选一个合得来的搭档就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一点  关于高野小姐的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.59,0:16:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你大概会成为副队长  所以应该是三佐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:30.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹰野三佐吗  实在是令人羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:41.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来介绍一下  这位是鹰野三佐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三佐  这位是入江京介医生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您…  您好  敝人入江
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用这么紧张  请坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.73,0:16:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看过关于雏见泽症候群的资料了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.32,0:17:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢  都是一些令人瞠目结舌的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且作为至今未被世界上的任何一个人解明的神秘事件
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:10.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大大的激起了我的求知欲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.70,0:17:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很吃惊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到像入江医生这么经验丰富的人居然会被埋没在诊疗室里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:25.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不介意的话  请务必让我接下这个研究
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你了  请多关照啊  入江所长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…才是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹰野小姐  我为你介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是富竹和小此木
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面  我是富竹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此次将担任这项任务的监督工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.06,0:17:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小此木
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.25,0:17:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是非正规战斗部队之一的「山狗」的队长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.67,0:18:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预定将常驻在雏见泽  对三佐进行支援
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.98,0:18:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以把他理解成保镖一样的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.11,0:18:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会成为三佐的左膀右臂  请尽情使唤我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.21,0:18:53.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈…妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.58,0:19:06.44,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（田无美代子(幼年三四)的爱好是收集儿童套餐上面的小旗  据说还差一个就收集到20个）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:21.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那边找
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:19:59.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神仙都是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:05.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么要受到这种折磨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.54,0:20:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底做错了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸说过  人生分为好事和坏事  无论哪边都不会持续太久
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.71,0:20:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这也不会持续很久吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:26.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就此把我的不幸结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我带来能够和至今为止的不幸相称的幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.14,0:20:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那也做不到的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.43,0:20:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不要这样的人生了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那道闪电把我劈死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.16,0:20:49.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田无美代子在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.32,0:20:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你夺走了我的爸爸妈妈那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的生命也从这里夺走啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:15.63,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}あなたの亡骸に土をかける
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:15.63,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}在你的遗骸上浇一把黑土
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:23.97,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}それが禁じられていたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:23.97,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}即便这是被禁止的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.62,0:21:32.53,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}純粋なまなざしの快楽には
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.62,0:21:32.53,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}在纯朴的目光里闪耀的快乐之中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.43,0:21:40.64,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}隠しきれない誘惑があった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.43,0:21:40.64,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}我看到了你心中无法隐藏的诱惑
