Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.24,0:23:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.04,0:23:06.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚收到岐阜的定期联络
